item.title: Analysis of Covid-19 Cases in Toronto
item.description: PartI. Abstract Covid-19 has had a huge influence on our daily life. The purpose of this project is to analysis covid-19 cases to find the age group of infected people, infection sources, hospital rate, etc. By analysis, close contact is the easiest way to get infected. Therefore it is imnportant to have self-protection. PartII. Introduction It has been over 9 months since the outbreak of COVID-19. As the data from Tencent news, more than 32 million people get infected, with over 980 thousand people died.
